### 🔋 Battery Life Prediction
**ML-powered system** predicting RUL & SOH of Li-ion batteries. Compares **9 algorithms** (XGBoost, LightGBM, Random Forest...) with real-time diagnostic GUI. Built for **ONEE x Huawei**.

